WEBVTT

00:01.151 --> 00:03.380
I got up early,
so I could figure out

00:03.381 --> 00:07.184
if there's anything around here
that I could stand living with.

00:07.218 --> 00:09.403
- You want to move in together?
- If the offer still stands.

00:09.437 --> 00:11.021
Are you kidding me?

00:11.055 --> 00:14.741
You slept with Quentin
while he was married to me.

00:14.776 --> 00:16.393
I asked you back then

00:16.411 --> 00:19.163
if anything had started
before we were separated.

00:19.197 --> 00:20.414
You said it hadn't.

00:20.448 --> 00:21.728
'Cause I didn't want
to hurt you.

00:21.732 --> 00:24.234
Here's
to your new partnership.

00:24.252 --> 00:25.669
I fronted your buy-in.

00:25.703 --> 00:27.171
How could you do that?

00:27.205 --> 00:29.289
I did it
as a romantic gesture.

00:29.340 --> 00:30.457
Yeah, well,<i>Pretty Woman</i>
may have been a romantic movie,

00:30.508 --> 00:31.959
but Julia Roberts
was still a hooker.

00:32.009 --> 00:33.710
How long have you known
Quentin had A.L.S.?

00:33.744 --> 00:34.962
From the beginning.

00:35.013 --> 00:36.773
And how long have you known
Quentin falsified

00:36.798 --> 00:39.016
trial results to get
the drug on the market?

00:39.050 --> 00:40.601
- He didn't lie.
- But you did.

00:40.635 --> 00:42.719
I love him.
So what else could I do?

00:42.753 --> 00:44.721
I am in this, Scottie.

00:44.755 --> 00:47.107
Okay.

00:47.141 --> 00:48.609
So am I.

00:48.643 --> 00:50.227
I think Mike Ross
went to a subpar law school

00:50.261 --> 00:51.728
and has been lying about it
the whole time.

00:51.762 --> 00:53.030
Just call up Harvard
and ask for a copy

00:53.064 --> 00:54.314
of his transcript.

00:54.365 --> 00:56.066
Professor Gerard's
legal ethics class,

00:56.100 --> 00:57.901
did you ever hear of anybody
ever getting an A-plus?

00:57.935 --> 00:59.987
No, he's famous for never
giving higher than an "A."

