Do you remember when you said
if Louis knew, we'd know?

06:44.601 --> 06:46.001
He knows.

06:46.019 --> 06:47.019
What did he do?

06:47.053 --> 06:48.520
He's bringing
in Henry Gerard

06:48.555 --> 06:50.189
